<h1>Apostell</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>Welcome to Apostell!</p>

<p>Apostell is a social community that aims to facilitate goods shipping to family, friends or acquaintances all over the globe.</p>

<p>Use your page to post about an item you're trying to send, or to let your friends know where you're travelling to, and carry something for them, or let them carry something for you.</p>

<p>All it takes is a sign up, follow people you know to receive their posts on your page, and sending your stuff around should be easier than ever before.</p>

<p>Click on the link below to activate your account:</p>

<%= link_to "Activate", edit_account_activation_url(@user.activation_token,
                                                    email: @user.email) %>
                                                    
<p>Thank you for choosing Apostell.</p>

<p>Yours faithfully,</p>

<p>Your Apostell team</p>